OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with some late sunshine; this
OL,7,Fmay turn hazy at times. Overnight,
OL,8,Fclear skies will persist, though the
OL,9,Fodd mist or fog patch possible towards
OL,10,Fdawn. Chilly in the countryside but
OL,11,Fnot as cold as recent nights.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FRemaining dry on Wednesday
OL,14,Fwith spells of sunshine, although
OL,15,Fperhaps cloudier than today,
OL,16,Fpotentially developing into sea fog
OL,17,Fnear coasts. Staying warm, especially
OL,18,Fin the south of the region.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
