OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FCooler and more changeable on
OL,7,FThursday, with spells of rain and
OL,8,Fshowers. Remaining unsettled on Friday
OL,9,Fand Saturday with further rain at
OL,10,Ftimes, mainly on Saturday.
OL,11,FTemperatures nearer to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
